item.title: Laura Izibor - Shine
item.description:
작곡: Laura Izibor / 작사: Words & Music by
KY: 79224

Wake up one morning
you realize
Your life is
one big compromise
Stuck
in the job
You swore was
only temporary
Feel like the world is
passing you by
Never done
all the things
You would need
to try
Stuck
in one place
Got a pain
in your face
From all
your stressing out
You ask
yourself
There’s got
to be more
Than what
I’m living for
You ask
yourself
There’s got
to be something else
Something more more
more
Well let the sunshine
on your face
And don’t let
your life go to waste
Now is
the time
Got to make up
your mind
Let it shine on you
let it shine on you
